r />\n<br />\n我覺得做呢份工人工少都算，做啲唔係倉務員做既事都算，最重要做得開心，但係呢兩日我根本失去了做人最基本的尊嚴。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 倉務員嗰個上司反而對我幾好，所以我唔明點解Sales部門主管可以鬧我，根本唔同部門。<br />\n<br />\n最後，希望我記住今日既感受，好多年之後都唔會變成佢咁既人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T17:01:20.000Z","msg":"轉工囉"},{"pid":"b09c8a061dd312ed3e173d408baf6c0fccf95ff8","tid":704096,"uid":35637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T17:04:33.000Z","msg":"走啦<br />\n唔係捱唔捱得的問題<br />\n係尊重問題<br />\n冇經濟負擔一定走"},{"pid":"eac8d418aef7382ec1a03bf6829e9722a2f941be","tid":704096,"uid":179117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T14:08:13.000Z","msg":"工已辭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到而家仲係有少少唔開心"},{"pid":"687e7accafaf750746c600746c7d77a61c2757bb","tid":704096,"uid":178332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T14:14:43.000Z","msg":"Bossini不嬲都係最賤最撚狗嘅工黎<br />\n返咗幾日趁早走<br />\n當自己冇返過算啦<br />\n但記得匿名投訴個賤人<br />\nEmail最好寫詳細啲<br />\n因為佢一日都係出糧嘅佢一日都重有阿頭<br />\n咪畀呢啲仆街以為自己可以隻手遮天<br />\n利申：有兩個朋友做過"},{"pid":"c2d237e741fd1eb03f2065848ce45f5e29e2f377","tid":704096,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T15:43:21.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},{"pid":"bdace93789312b5baf05013995eac1486c38fa8a","tid":704096,"uid":62289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T15:48:37.000Z","msg":"邊區 邊間"},{"pid":"dc669b034fdd64b9f7f4b63b17da4df4f12ae225","tid":704096,"uid":179117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T15:52:26.000Z","msg":"間嘢係綠色線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}